  <header><h1>School Supply Publisher</h1></header>
  <nav>
    <a href="publisher_valid.html">Valid Order</a>
    <a href="publisher_duplicate.html">Duplicate Message</a>
    <a href="publisher_invalid.html">Invalid Payloads</a>
    <a href="help.html">Help</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>How to Use</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Open one of the pages (Valid / Duplicate / Invalid).</li>
      <li>Click <b>Generate JSON</b> → <b>Copy JSON</b>.</li>
      <li>In Google Cloud Console, go to <b>Pub/Sub → Topics → your topic → Publish message</b>.</li>
      <li>Paste the JSON into the message body, then click <b>Publish</b>.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>What You’ll Test</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Valid orders get saved and shown by your subscriber/UI.</li>
      <li>Duplicate messages (same <code>event_id</code>) are detected.</li>
      <li>Invalid payloads are rejected (no bad rows in DB).</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
